text:
Today, Tenka is...
really fired up...!

Yesterday... with Naa-chan and Chiyuki-san...
we had delicious cake...!

Haha, that sounds nice.
What kind of cake did you have?

Um...
It was a limited edition one with lots of fruits...!

There were many different cakes...
Tenka had... a hard time choosing...

Both Naa-chan and Chiyuki-san... when they
saw the fruit cake... they were like, "That looks good"...

So... hehe...
the three of us had matching cakes...!
